column3:
If anyone testing this gets stuck running `./configure` and/or doesn't want to pass `disable-dependency-tracking`, a workaround is to downgrade automake to `1.15.1`. See my comment [here](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/14404#issuecomment-431542526) for more info.
